00:41:41.760 --> 00:41:44.310
than just saying, well,
we do perf for six months,

00:41:44.310 --> 00:41:46.390
we do an annual
review, whatever.

00:41:46.390 --> 00:41:49.720
That's the way to accomplish
the objective with less

00:41:49.720 --> 00:41:52.320
energy than does this?

00:41:52.320 --> 00:41:54.496
But the ROI on this is
significantly better,

00:41:54.496 --> 00:41:56.870
I believe, because you're
training people on how to do it

00:41:56.870 --> 00:41:58.570
and you're giving
it more frequently.

00:41:58.570 --> 00:41:59.990
AUDIENCE: We can
