conversation about what parts

00:42:17.020 --> 00:42:19.100
of it we should use and
what parts we shouldn't.

00:42:19.100 --> 00:42:21.612
And as the nature of work
evolves, a lot of it's

00:42:21.612 --> 00:42:22.820
going to fall by the wayside.

00:42:22.820 --> 00:42:25.550
But that doesn't mean we
have to stop doing it.

00:42:25.550 --> 00:42:28.420
It means we have to say, what
does management look like?

00:42:28.420 --> 00:42:29.740
How do we innovate the factory?

00:42:29.740 --> 00:42:31.572
We can't just let
it be free-range,

00:42:31.572 --> 00:42:32.530
but how do we innovate?

00:42:32.530 --> 00:42:33.655
What do we replace it with?

00:42:33.655 --> 00:42:34.660
Absolutely.

